  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the powers of your flashlight to light up the shadow creatures that roam trought the forest and seek your way out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3c1fd77a208ecca9d61e8f831c7637fc.apng?t=1731638988\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3c1fd77a208ecca9d61e8f831c7637fc.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=96 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the flashlight as your main weapon of defeating the shadow creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, dodge or counter the bullet hell-like attacks of all your enemies to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain Light Drops by defeating enemies to become stronger or use them to buy items, upgrades and costumes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through the 5 areas of the forest to find your way out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat strong enemies to rescue the spirits of children trapped in the shadow's realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the secret pages hidden throught the forest to learn more about events that transpired before your arrival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new powers and use them to clear puzzles blocking your path.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" width=566 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.webm?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.mp4?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Have you ever heard stories of monsters living under the bed?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- What about legends of shadow figures who kidnap inocent children?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a quiet night like any other, a little girl had the misfortune of experiencing the visit of a shadow being - The Forgotten - and is taken to a dark forest in the realm of this creature. Now she has to find a way out before the shadows take her soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate throught the forest with help of your new friends, fight with a magical flashlight to be your light and learn about the fate of your long lost sister and her sudden disapearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.webm?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.mp4?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the powers of your flashlight to light up the shadow creatures that roam trought the forest and seek your way out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3c1fd77a208ecca9d61e8f831c7637fc.apng?t=1731638988\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3c1fd77a208ecca9d61e8f831c7637fc.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=96 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the flashlight as your main weapon of defeating the shadow creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, dodge or counter the bullet hell-like attacks of all your enemies to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain Light Drops by defeating enemies to become stronger or use them to buy items, upgrades and costumes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through the 5 areas of the forest to find your way out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat strong enemies to rescue the spirits of children trapped in the shadow's realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the secret pages hidden throught the forest to learn more about events that transpired before your arrival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new powers and use them to clear puzzles blocking your path.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" width=566 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.webm?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/8018886348b37f049266d65a78eaf810.mp4?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Have you ever heard stories of monsters living under the bed?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- What about legends of shadow figures who kidnap inocent children?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a quiet night like any other, a little girl had the misfortune of experiencing the visit of a shadow being - The Forgotten - and is taken to a dark forest in the realm of this creature. Now she has to find a way out before the shadows take her soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate throught the forest with help of your new friends, fight with a magical flashlight to be your light and learn about the fate of your long lost sister and her sudden disapearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.poster.avif?t=1731638988\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.webm?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208220/extras/3921d090f5d8b80324044c278992eec8.mp4?t=1731638988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
